    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Fixing Psych::SyntaxError When Using Jekyll]]></title>
    <link href="http://joshrendek.com/2012/08/fixing-psych-syntaxerror-when-using-jekyll/"/>
    <updated>2012-08-19T15:30:00-04:00</updated>
    <id>http://joshrendek.com/2012/08/fixing-psych-syntaxerror-when-using-jekyll</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I was working on my blog and moving some posts around when I kept getting a Psych::SyntaxError when generating it with Jekyll and ruby 1.9.x. Unfortunately the default stack trace doesn&rsquo;t provide much information on what file was causing the issue, so a quick way to find out is opening up irb:</p>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Example to run in irb - sample.rb </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="nb">require</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">lsquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">yaml</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rsquo</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="no">Dir</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">foreach</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">source</span><span class="o">/&lt;</span><span class="n">em</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">posts</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">each</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="o">|</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="o">|</span> <span class="no">YAML</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">load_file</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">source</span><span class="o">/&lt;</span><span class="sr">/em&gt;posts/</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">f</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">unless</span> <span class="n">f</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">&amp;rdquo</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="o">||</span> <span class="n">f</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">.</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rdquo</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>
]]></content>
